{
  "id": "69bb3d1e3f890b11bac836a4",
  "title": "彝語の単語リストを彝文字に変換する",
  "created": 1773878562,
  "updated": 1773887051,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bb3d1e3f890b11bac836a4",
      "text": "彝語の単語リストを彝文字に変換する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878562,
      "updated": 1773878593
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3d21000000000068474c",
      "text": "[彝語]、([ꆈꌠ], [Nuosu], [ヌオス語]) の単語リストを見つけた。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878562,
      "updated": 1773878712
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3db30000000000684752",
      "text": " [https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Yi_(Mihei)_word_list Appendix:Yi (Mihei) word list - Wiktionary, the free dictionary]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878708,
      "updated": 1773878708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3d22000000000068474d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878563,
      "updated": 1773878620
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3dae0000000000684750",
      "text": "単語がアルファベットで綴られており、彝文字で書かれていない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878702,
      "updated": 1773878806
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3e150000000000684755",
      "text": "これらを彝文字に変換することで彝語の雰囲気を感じてみよう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878806,
      "updated": 1773878806
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3e100000000000684753",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878800,
      "updated": 1773878800
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3e100000000000684754",
      "text": "単語リストに現れる謎の上付き数字は声調を表すと考えられる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878800,
      "updated": 1773879201
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4cef00000000006847e1",
      "text": "\t概要",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882608,
      "updated": 1773882620
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4cfb00000000006847e2",
      "text": "\t\t殆ど全ての上付き数字は 2 文字で 1 組を成し、彝語の声調の数字表現と一致するため、声調を表すものと考えられる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882620,
      "updated": 1773882714
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3e8a000000000068475e",
      "text": "\t詳細",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878923,
      "updated": 1773882624
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4cfd00000000006847e3",
      "text": " \t現れるトークンを洗い出す",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882621,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb422e000000000068476e",
      "text": "  \t²¹、³³、⁴⁴、⁵⁵ がある。計 4312 件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879855,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3f440000000000684761",
      "text": "  \t\t²¹:  925件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879109,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3f4d0000000000684764",
      "text": "  \t\t³³:  2294件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879118,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3f4e0000000000684765",
      "text": "  \t\t⁴⁴:  421件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879119,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3f4b0000000000684763",
      "text": "  \t\t⁵⁵:  672件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879115,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3ed7000000000068475f",
      "text": "   \tそれ以外のものは 6 件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878999,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb401f0000000000684766",
      "text": "    \t274b\t脱(发)\t¹ɿ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879327,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb40990000000000684768",
      "text": "    \t557\t叫(狗)\tvo⁵ ⁵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879449,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb409e0000000000684769",
      "text": "    \t506\t一秒钟\ttshɿ²¹¹ɔ³³zɯ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879455,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb40890000000000684767",
      "text": "    \t711\t一千七百四十二\ttshɿ²¹tu³³ʂʅ⁴⁴ha³²¹ɿ³³tshi³³ȵi⁴⁴",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879434,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb40de000000000068476a",
      "text": "    \t1805\t粗细\ta³³fu⁴⁴ɪ⁵ ⁵ fu³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879518,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb410a000000000068476c",
      "text": "    \t1868\t大路\tta⁵6ka³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879563,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3ede0000000000684760",
      "text": "    \t4312 件の整ったトークンに対して、6件しかない例外であること、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879006,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4151000000000068476d",
      "text": "    \t全ての例外に対して書き損じる前の物が想定できるため、これらは全て誤字であると考えられる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879634,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb42a30000000000684770",
      "text": "   正規トークンを、²¹、³³、⁴⁴、⁵⁵ とする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879972,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb42b50000000000684771",
      "text": "   誤字トークンをそれ以外とする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879990,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb42c00000000000684772",
      "text": "   \t具体的には　¹、⁵ ⁵、²¹¹、³²¹、⁵6　がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880000,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb3db00000000000684751",
      "text": "  予想：音節の末尾にトークンが付与されていることから、トークンは声調であろうことが伺える。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773878704,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb424e000000000068476f",
      "text": "  確定：[https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/彝语北部方言#声调 彝语北部方言#声调] に声調の数字表現リストがあり、発見された正規トークンと完全に一致するため、トークンは声調であると考えられる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773879886,
      "updated": 1773882627
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43220000000000684774",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880099,
      "updated": 1773880133
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43460000000000684777",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880135,
      "updated": 1773880135
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43500000000000684778",
      "text": "誤字トークンを正規トークンに修正する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880145,
      "updated": 1773880196
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4b5600000000006847c3",
      "text": "\t概要",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882199,
      "updated": 1773882206
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4b6b00000000006847c5",
      "text": "\t\ttable:修正前後",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882220,
      "updated": 1773882229
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4b8300000000006847c7",
      "text": "\t\t \t\t修正前\t修正後",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882244,
      "updated": 1773882251
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4b7900000000006847c6",
      "text": "\t \t274b\t脱(发)\t¹ɿ³³\tlɿ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882233,
      "updated": 1773882243
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4b9300000000006847c9",
      "text": "\t \t557\t叫(狗)\tvo⁵ ⁵\tvo⁵⁵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882259,
      "updated": 1773882269
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4b8c00000000006847c8",
      "text": "\t \t506\t一秒钟\ttshɿ²¹¹ɔ³³zɯ³³\ttshɿ²¹lɔ³³zɯ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882253,
      "updated": 1773882289
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4bc100000000006847ca",
      "text": "\t \t711\t一千七百四十二\ttshɿ²¹tu³³ʂʅ⁴⁴ha³²¹ɿ³³tshi³³ȵi⁴⁴\ttshɿ²¹tu³³ʂʅ⁴⁴ha³²¹ɿ³³tshi³³ȵi⁴⁴",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882305,
      "updated": 1773882319
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4bf400000000006847cc",
      "text": "\t \t1805\t粗细\ta³³fu⁴⁴ɪ⁵ ⁵ fu³³\ta³³fu⁴⁴ɪ⁵⁵ fu³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882357,
      "updated": 1773882371
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4c0b00000000006847cd",
      "text": "\t \t1868\t大路\tta⁵6ka³³\tta⁵⁵ka³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882380,
      "updated": 1773882389
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4b5e00000000006847c4",
      "text": "\t詳細",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882206,
      "updated": 1773882233
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43450000000000684776",
      "text": " \t274b\t脱(发)\t¹ɿ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880133,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43aa000000000068477f",
      "text": " \t\ttable:274bに類似した単語",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880235,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43b50000000000684780",
      "text": "   \t274\t脱\tlu⁵⁵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880246,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43b60000000000684781",
      "text": "    274a\t脱(皮)\tlu²¹",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880246,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb43b60000000000684782",
      "text": "    274b\t脱(发)\t¹ɿ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880246,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb47ac00000000006847b6",
      "text": " \t\tこれはおそらく l が 1 に書き間違えられたもので、元は lɿ³³ だろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881261,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb438b0000000000684779",
      "text": " \t557\t叫(狗)\tvo⁵ ⁵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880204,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45470000000000684787",
      "text": " \t\ttable:557に類似した単語",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880648,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb453c0000000000684786",
      "text": "  \t\t557\t叫(狗)\tvo⁵ ⁵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880637,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb46b600000000006847b0",
      "text": "    557a\t叫(猪、马、羊)\te³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881014,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb46b600000000006847b1",
      "text": "    557b\t叫(鸟、狼、)\tʂʅ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881014,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb46b600000000006847b2",
      "text": "    557c\t叫(牛、)\tmbu³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881014,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb46b600000000006847b3",
      "text": "    557D\t叫(鸡)\tɔ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881014,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45040000000000684785",
      "text": "   \t1016\t狗叫\tkhɯ³³vo⁵⁵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880581,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb472f00000000006847b5",
      "text": "   \t103\t公鸡(未鸣叫)\tva³³tɕho⁵⁵pu³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881136,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb472200000000006847b4",
      "text": "   \t1057\t牛叫\tlɯ³³bu³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881123,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb47cb00000000006847b7",
      "text": " \t\tこれはおそらくスペースが入り込んだ vo⁵⁵ だろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881292,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb438b000000000068477a",
      "text": " \t506\t一秒钟\ttshɿ²¹¹ɔ³³zɯ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880204,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45840000000000684797",
      "text": " \t\ttable:506に類似した単語",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880709,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb457b0000000000684788",
      "text": "  \t\t502\t一辈子\ttshɿ²¹zɿ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880699,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45800000000000684790",
      "text": "    503\t一代\ttshɿ²¹tshɿ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880704,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45800000000000684791",
      "text": "    504\t半小时\tthɯ³³kho²¹ɡu⁴⁴pha³³ma³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880704,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45800000000000684792",
      "text": "    505\t一小时\tthɯ³³kho²¹ma³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880704,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45800000000000684793",
      "text": "    506\t一秒钟\ttshɿ²¹¹ɔ³³zɯ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880704,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45800000000000684794",
      "text": "    507\t一分钟\ttshɿ²¹ɡu⁵⁵zɯ³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880704,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45800000000000684795",
      "text": "    508\t星期(礼拜)\tɕi³³tɕhɿ²¹",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880704,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45800000000000684796",
      "text": "    509\t初一\tdɔ³³tshɿ²¹ȵi²¹",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880704,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb47f700000000006847b8",
      "text": " \t\tこれは 1 が重複しており、元は tshɿ²¹ɔ³³zɯ³³ であるか、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881336,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb488e00000000006847ba",
      "text": " \t\tおそらく l が 1 に書き間違えられたもので、元は tshɿ²¹lɔ³³zɯ³³ であろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773881487,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb4bd700000000006847cb",
      "text": " \t\t\t類似の誤字が多いため、此方を採用する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773882328,
      "updated": 1773882343
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb438b000000000068477b",
      "text": " \t711\t一千七百四十二\ttshɿ²¹tu³³ʂʅ⁴⁴ha³²¹ɿ³³tshi³³ȵi⁴⁴",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880204,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb45dc0000000000684798",
      "text": " \t\ttable:711に類似した単語",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880797,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb463000000000006847a8",
      "text": " \t\t 678\t一\ttshɿ²¹",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880880,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb462700000000006847a7",
      "text": " \t\t 679\t二\tȵi²¹",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880872,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb461e00000000006847a6",
      "text": " \t\t 681\t四\tlu³³",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773880863,
      "updated": 1773882215
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb461600000000006847a5",
